 rв†ђUpload(author name source avatar);lines;tmpns;ns;overwritten;dir;path;meta;ens
вЌќ Upload a user bot: validate, save to disk, install into runtime
 вЋ•IOв†ђ0
 вЌќ Reject if name matches a built-in
 :If 0в‰ ##.Rhobots.вЋ•NCвЉ‚name
     вЋ•SIGNALвЉ‚('EN' 11)('Message'('Name conflicts with built-in bot: ',name))
 :EndIf
 вЌќ Validate source by fixing into a temp namespace
 linesв†ђ(вЋ•UCS 10)(в‰ вЉ†вЉў)source
 tmpnsв†ђвЋ•NS''
 :Trap 0
     2 tmpns.вЋ•FIX lines
 :Else
     вЋ•SIGNALвЉ‚('EN' 11)('Message'('Source failed to fix: ',вЋ•DMX.Message))
 :EndTrap
 вЌќ Check Init and Tick exist with correct valence
 nsв†ђtmpnsвЌЋname
 :If 3в‰ ns.вЋ•NC'Init'
     вЋ•SIGNALвЉ‚('EN' 11)('Message' 'Bot must define Init as a function')
 :EndIf
 :If 3в‰ ns.вЋ•NC'Tick'
     вЋ•SIGNALвЉ‚('EN' 11)('Message' 'Bot must define Tick as a function')
 :EndIf
 вЌќ Check overwrite
 pathв†ђ##.Cfg.USER_BOTS_PATH,'/',author,'/',name,'.apln'
 overwrittenв†ђвЋ•NEXISTS path
 вЌќ Ensure author dir exists and write files
 dirв†ђ##.Cfg.USER_BOTS_PATH,'/',author
 3 вЋ•MKDIR dir
 (вЉ‚source)вЋ•NPUT path 1
 :If (вЋ•NULLв‰Ўavatar)в€Ё(0=в‰ўavatar)
     avatarв†ђ''
 :EndIf
 metaв†ђвЋ•JSON(author: author в‹„ created: (вЌ•вЋ•TS) в‹„ avatar: avatar)
 (вЉ‚meta)вЋ•NPUT(dir,'/',name,'.json')1
 вЌќ Install into runtime
 :If 0=##.вЋ•NC'UserBots'
     'UserBots'##.вЋ•NS''
 :EndIf
 :If 0=##.UserBots.вЋ•NCвЉ‚author
     author ##.UserBots.вЋ•NS''
 :EndIf
 ensв†ђ##.UserBotsвЌЋauthor
 2 ens.вЋ•FIX lines
 rв†ђ(name: name в‹„ author: author в‹„ overwritten: overwritten)
